    <span class="eyebrow">About</span>
    <h1 class="display">About Love Your Senses</h1>
    <p class="sub">The idea behind the quizzes, and who is behind them.</p>
  </div></section>

  <section class="content"><div class="wrap"><div class="prose">
    <p>Love Your Senses began with a simple frustration. Finding a fragrance, or almost anything you wear or use, usually means wading through endless listings and reviews written for everyone and no one in particular. We thought there was a kinder way to do it.</p>
    <p>So we build short, enjoyable quizzes that get to know your taste in a minute, then point you toward the things that genuinely suit you. We are starting with fragrance, where the right scent is such a personal thing, and expanding across the senses from there, into skincare, sleep, taste and more.</p>
    <p>We are an independent site based in the United Kingdom. Every recommendation is chosen on merit, because it fits the result you get, never because of who pays the most.</p>
    <p>When you buy through some of our links we may earn a small commission, at no extra cost to you. That is what keeps the quizzes free to take. You can read more on our <a href="/disclosure">Affiliate Disclosure</a> page.</p>
    <p>Have an idea for a quiz, or a question for us? We would love to hear from you at <a href="mailto:hello@loveyoursenses.com">hello@loveyoursenses.com</a>.</p>
    <div class="cta-row"><a href="/scent" class="btn">Take the scent quiz</a></div>
  </div></div></section>
